类 JSON

java.lang.Object
java.util.AbstractMap<K,V>
java.util.HashMap<String,Object>
org.giiwa.json.JSON
所有已实现的接口:
Serializable, Cloneable, Comparable<JSON>, Map<String,Object>
public final class JSON extends HashMap<String,Object> implements Comparable<JSON>, Cloneable
The Class JSON, simple JSON object, using Gson to parse and format,
and find api by xpath
